    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Feature</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span>Upload Backups via Console 2nd release (UI and Backup Service improvements)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bug</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix Add autocomplete=\"off\" for login form (W.11)</li>\n<li>Fix Properly delete secret references on service deletion</li>\n<li>Fix Improve efficiency of listUsers</li>\n<li>Fix Deployment failure - Uncaught TypeError 'length' of undefined</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Improvement</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Upgrade partially encrypt algorithm to AES-256</li>\n<li>Update deployment status code to read workload instead of pod</li>\n</ul>"
      },
